{"tid":123123,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你所認識既我一直都唔存在","createTime":"2017-02-16T14:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T10:03:27.000Z","uid":51543,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"818f661a659661ce6627cce7477f5e0edcc40d92","tid":123123,"uid":51543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:54:02.000Z","msg":"平時好似好friendly,好nice,有講有笑，派下膠咁，其實私底下唔鐘意笑，好陰沉，唔想理人咁多，日日做第二個人其實真係好辛苦，我想做返自己，但跟本無可能，人就係咁，呢個社會同身邊既人都唔可能接受真正既我。慢慢我覺得身邊都好虛偽，其實都係飾演緊另一個人，平時對住你笑，好開朗，私底下可能好恐怖，笑鳩你；平時好人好者，內心可能恨不得你死；無人可以同自己交心，就算有，自己都係聆聽者，唔會透露自己半點內心。我知道有唔少人都係咁，希望大家好好飾演呢個角色。"},{"pid":"f245e87d406fa915e8ba2b0fdebfb794eab2d2de","tid":123123,"uid":83250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f989643518f2a55cd0dd4b30fbb1d6d34bd144e","tid":123123,"uid":51543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6807b8361a302dcaa4eb6a0ddd38547c76b7d999","tid":123123,"uid":51543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:38:10.000Z","msg":"比正皮既巴絲們加油"},{"pid":"95128fbfa31253c7e6da6f7c3db650602867af1c","tid":123123,"uid":78018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:35:57.000Z","msg":"咁樣做人好辛苦喎巴打 你有冇朋友？"},{"pid":"213a5b9086b70f615a065416e756c887ec603471","tid":123123,"uid":51543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樣做人好辛苦喎巴打 你有冇朋友？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有不過唔多交心下，就算傾心事都係做聆聽者"},{"pid":"22af8323643868a37863549656c47d18051bebca","tid":123123,"uid":26559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"